summary: I mean, Paul, Ewan and Evie are amazing most of the time, cos they escape, they they get engrossed in things like we never can,...
body:
I mean, Paul, Ewan and Evie are amazing most of the time, cos they escape, they they get engrossed in things like we never can, or if we did, we’d look mad. Talking to little plastic figures two inches from your face.

Dave Tiler (Single Father Episode 1)

summary: I’ve never seen nor read Much Ado About Nothing before watching the David Tennant/Catherine Tate version just now and let me...
